## Delivery Plan

### Phase 1 — Foundation + Core (Tasks, Agents, Notifications)
- MCP server scaffold, Supabase client, tool registration system
- Tasks (7 tools), Agents (6 tools), Notifications (5 tools)
- **18 tools total** — the most commonly needed features

### Phase 2 — Orchestration (Scheduler, Workflows, Chat)
- Scheduler (6 tools), Workflows (8 tools), Chat (6 tools)
- **20 tools** — execution and communication layer

### Phase 3 — Intelligence (Summit, Projects, Knowledge, Telemetry)
- Summit (5 tools), Projects (5 tools), Knowledge (5 tools), Telemetry (3 tools)
- **18 tools** — context and intelligence

### Phase 4 — Meta & Gamification (Audit, Prompt Chunks, MCP, Connections, Gamification)
- Audit (2 tools), Prompt Chunks (4 tools), MCP Servers (4 tools), Connections (4 tools), Gamification (5 tools)
- **19 tools** — configuration and meta-management

