## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `npx tsc --noEmit` to verify TypeScript compilation
- Test each tool individually using the MCP inspector: `npx @modelcontextprotocol/inspector`
- Verify data round-trips: create → read → update → delete for each domain

### Manual Verification
- Install MCP in one OpenClaw agent and issue tool calls
- Confirm dashboard UI updates in real-time when agent creates/updates tasks
- Verify all 70+ tools are discoverable via `tools/list`
